{"tid":1300994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請推！2/7做了選民，有票未必有得投","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:18:55.000Z","uid":264331,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9726d7e5b08a75d07125ed351bcd86124473eaa2","tid":1300994,"uid":264331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:50:20.000Z","msg":"上屆區議會選舉一共有68區由建制派自動當選，近60萬市民「有票冇得投」！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQS23ga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQS23ga.png&h=6eda917c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">代表咩？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你2/7做了選民，都未必有得投</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要反自動當選先可以削減建制派勢力！</span></span><br />\n區議會選舉將於11月24日舉行<br />\n提名期定為 2019 年 10 月 4 日至 17 日<br />\n代表現在大家就要凖備，要揾人參選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAhRWD1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAhRWD1.png&h=127f8fbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得此乃持久戰，俾建制派自動當選，我地一番心機就白費哂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">血債票償</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見好多關於區議會的post都沉左底<br />\n選區議員對持久戰黎講，真的好重要！！！"},{"pid":"1a231e2a1100911563d9e034aae3a20cd23d042d","tid":1300994,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"其實真係要搵人選<br />\n有冇咩專業人士出黎選下 空降都可能贏<br />\n至少俾機會我哋投"},{"pid":"a7dd82de0de32d6ef3c838b319e644c2568ee560","tid":1300994,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"14e815e01099fac83828b581d464ac790900eb41","tid":1300994,"uid":264331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a231e2a1100911563d9e034aae3a20cd23d042d","tid":1300994,"uid":143151,"